reviews.text: The chicken wings are worth ordering. As for the rest, depends on your personal taste..
Taste good. Will visit again.

Food is fair, but service is not good enough. One of my dishes (roasted shrimp) was missed order but the staff pretended the delay was caused of the cooking time. We had waited for nearly 1 hour and really feel frustrated about it. Frustrated about it.
Good taste , price reason
Japanese style with Sichuan twist, good draft beer. Veggies were the best part of the night. Cool vibes, great staff, small plates just keep ordering.

result.name: 川燒

reviews.text: The chicken wings are worth ordering. As for the rest, depends on your personal taste..
味道算比一般街邊串燒好味 但唔平 如果真係食飽同食得好可能一個人要三四百起跳
味道唔錯但價錢真係唔平，咁嘅味道咁嘅價錢可以有更好嘅選擇
依間野味道算幾唔錯，喺呢個地方食串燒個價錢算係適中，不過份量有啲小。大家可以一試佢嗰個蘋果雪葩 真係幾好食。 依期食完會有50蚊coupon。
渡船街一帶是燒烤跟夜宵的好地方，川燒只用簡單白調味已帶出食品的美味😍
